  "body": "As a user\r\nI want to connected to the closet waku node\r\nSo that I can retrieve messages faster\r\n\r\n### Problem\r\n\r\nWaku nodes will be located in different geographical reason, likely there will be a tangible performance difference by connecting to the closest node available.\r\n\r\nA client should connect to the closest node available by ping time, and should prefer connecting to that node if available.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance criteria\r\n\r\n* Upon connecting/reconnecting to a node, a client should always prefer the fastest node (measured in ping time) if available.\r\n* Any re-connection mechanism should be using this option if implemented  ( https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9466 )\r\n\r\nDepends on https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9465",
